1
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:16,200
Official uniform style.

2
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:17,590
Prefect of Yunzhou,

3
00:01:17,860 --> 00:01:18,460
Gu Wenyuan.

4
00:01:18,460 --> 00:01:19,920
The corpse doesn't decay.

5
00:01:19,930 --> 00:01:21,530
The jade marrow has a spirit.

6
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:28,060
Lin Yan,

7
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,620
do you know Prefect Gu?

8
00:01:31,730 --> 00:01:32,229
I...

9
00:01:32,330 --> 00:01:33,430
When I saw this face,

10
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:34,300
my heart suddenly ached.

11
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:34,759
It seems

12
00:01:34,930 --> 00:01:35,789
like I know him.

13
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:37,360
But I can't remember.

14
00:01:41,860 --> 00:01:42,560
This mark

15
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:44,500
has been here for 7 years.

16
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,759
But I don't remember how I got it.

17
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,560
This room is sealed.

18
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,460
It is only connected

19
00:01:53,460 --> 00:01:54,630
to the outside through the underwater passage.

20
00:01:54,630 --> 00:01:55,830
Gu Wenyuan passed away here in meditation,

21
00:01:55,830 --> 00:01:57,000
there must be a deep meaning.

22
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,330
Let's search carefully

23
00:01:58,630 --> 00:02:00,360
to see if there are other clues.

24
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:02,030
Miss Xiaocui,

25
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:04,730
do you happen to know this place?

26
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,430
I exhausted my efforts in mystical arts

27
00:02:10,430 --> 00:02:12,700
and obtained the fragments of the Nine Turns Reincarnation.

28
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:13,860
Only then did I know that in this world,

29
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:16,860
there's an evil method of seizing bodies to extend life.

30
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:18,190
It's too late to regret.

31
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,620
Prefect Gu,

32
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:21,760
I am Shen Mo,

33
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:24,230
son of Shen Qingshan from the Criminal Investigation Department.

34
00:02:24,230 --> 00:02:25,730
I've tracked a bizarre case here.

35
00:02:25,730 --> 00:02:27,360
I hope the Prefect's spirit in heaven

36
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,960
can help me uncover the truth

37
00:02:29,100 --> 00:02:30,230
to comfort the dead.

38
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,100
The material is the same,

39
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:42,200
but the degree of nourishment is different.

40
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:44,130
The one at the morgue had thin blood veins.

41
00:02:44,130 --> 00:02:44,800
This one

42
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:46,460
feels warm like holding warm jade.

43
00:02:46,460 --> 00:02:47,829
The blood veins have formed a net.

44
00:02:47,829 --> 00:02:48,300
It seems

45
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:49,730
it has been nourished for a long time.

46
00:02:49,730 --> 00:02:51,300
There are very fine cracks inside.

47
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:52,100
At the cracks,

48
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:53,960
there seem to be shadows flowing.

49
00:03:05,530 --> 00:03:06,300
Latecomers.

50
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:07,600
I am Gu Wenyuan.

51
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:09,060
My daughter Zijin is not dead.

52
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,660
I used the Turtle Breath Pill and the Soul Sealing Talisman

53
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:11,400
to make her feign death,

54
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:13,500
and hid her in the ice coffin on the lower level.

55
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,530
But I am exhausted.

56
00:03:14,530 --> 00:03:15,500
The evil array has been set.

57
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:17,600
Qin Muzhi conspired with a noble in the palace

58
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:18,500
to use the array

59
00:03:18,730 --> 00:03:19,700
to alter the nation's destiny

60
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:21,030
and extend their lives.

61
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,360
Be careful.

62
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:26,530
Qin Muzhi is not the mastermind.

63
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:28,930
There is a mastermind behind him.

64
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:30,100
Qintian...

65
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:32,920
The remnant soul is bound.

66
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:37,130
This array is still running.

67
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,300
There's an ice cellar below.

68
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,690
Gu Zijin should be in it.

69
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:55,660
My lord.

70
00:03:55,930 --> 00:03:56,860
Beware of traps.

71
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,500
Gu Wenyuan's remnant soul is bound.

72
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,300
What he said shouldn't be false.

73
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,690
Seven years.

74
00:04:11,930 --> 00:04:13,460
The body is still so well-preserved.

75
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,260
The complexion looks alive.

76
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:15,800
The coffin is made of special cold jade,

77
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,100
which can keep the body from decaying.

78
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:18,300
What an exquisite technique,

79
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:19,260
and so dangerous.

80
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:20,120
This talisman.

81
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:22,290
It's not just soul sealing.

82
00:04:22,530 --> 00:04:24,790
It also draws souls and gathers spirits.

83
00:04:25,230 --> 00:04:27,160
She is being nourished as a vessel.

84
00:04:27,230 --> 00:04:28,560
Once the array is activated,

85
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,530
another's soul will be forcibly injected into her body,

86
00:04:30,530 --> 00:04:31,390
to replace her.

87
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:33,500
There is a mastermind behind Qin Muzhi,

88
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:35,100
and it involves the Qintian.

89
00:04:35,530 --> 00:04:37,590
Could it be the Qintian Directorate?

90
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:47,960
Who are you?

91
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,260
Where is my father?

92
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:49,860
Miss Gu,

93
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,430
I am Shen Mo, Registrar of the Penal Bureau.

94
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:53,760
Your father, Prefect Gu Wenyuan,

95
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:55,760
has already passed away in meditation outside.

96
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,159
We found you here,

97
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:57,960
sleeping.

98
00:04:58,530 --> 00:04:59,560
Sleeping...

99
00:05:00,260 --> 00:05:01,060
Father said

100
00:05:01,460 --> 00:05:03,120
he would take me to a safe place

101
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,560
to wait for his return.

102
00:05:05,530 --> 00:05:07,630
My head hurts. So many voices.

103
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,260
He said my father would be resurrected,

104
00:05:10,830 --> 00:05:12,230
and we would be reunited.

105
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,130
Miss Gu,

106
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:15,460
is there a spell on your left arm?

107
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,460
Do you remember

108
00:05:16,660 --> 00:05:17,800
who drew it for you?

109
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:27,200
You are here to stop my father from resurrecting.

110
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:28,960
You are enemies!

111
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,630
You've been placed under a Soul Control Contract or a similar spell.

112
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,760
Your memories have been tampered with.

113
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:33,230
Miss Gu,

114
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:34,200
wake up!

115
00:05:34,460 --> 00:05:35,460
Prefect Gu has passed away.

116
00:05:35,460 --> 00:05:36,560
He wanted you to live,

117
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,760
not become a vessel for another's soul.

118
00:05:39,330 --> 00:05:39,930
Lies!

119
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,159
Father will definitely return!

120
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:44,400
Miss Gu,

121
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:44,930
listen to me.

122
00:05:44,930 --> 00:05:46,230
Seven years ago, your father Gu Wenyuan

123
00:05:46,230 --> 00:05:47,530
discovered the evil Nine Cycles Reincarnation Array,

124
00:05:47,530 --> 00:05:48,000
and was murdered.

125
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:50,130
His body is in the upper stone chamber.

126
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,400
Think carefully.

127
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:51,960
In your memory,

128
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,159
is your father's promise to you

129
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:54,600
always blurry?

130
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,530
Is there always a voice

131
00:05:55,530 --> 00:05:56,030
telling you

132
00:05:56,030 --> 00:05:56,960
what to believe?

133
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:58,100
This spell is not only for control,

134
00:05:58,100 --> 00:06:00,230
but also for monitoring and tracking.

135
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:12,230
The spell is temporarily suppressed.

136
00:06:12,230 --> 00:06:12,960
Miss Gu,

137
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:14,830
can you remember anything now?

138
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:22,100
Lin Yan.

139
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:23,460
Brother,

140
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:24,860
is that you?

141
00:06:25,130 --> 00:06:25,400
You

142
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:26,700
recognize me?

143
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,000
On your arm,

144
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,460
is there a mark?

145
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:32,200
They planted a Master Pact on me.

146
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,130
Brother Lin Yan.

147
00:06:35,330 --> 00:06:36,060
The one on you

148
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,960
is a Subordinate Pact,

149
00:06:39,130 --> 00:06:40,330
controlled by me.

150
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:42,100
Mr. Shen.

151
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,600
Before my father died,

152
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,930
he asked me to pass a message to Uncle Shen Qingshan,

153
00:06:44,930 --> 00:06:45,760
just one sentence.

154
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,159
The Nine Cycles are not reincarnation,

155
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:48,130
the Dragon Vein devours souls.

156
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:49,630
On the ninth floor of the Qintian Directorate,

157
00:06:49,630 --> 00:06:51,159
someone is waiting for you.

158
00:06:51,330 --> 00:06:52,300
Unfortunately,

159
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,230
I couldn't meet Uncle Shen.

160
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:55,560
Mo'er.

161
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,230
That pagoda has nine stories,

162
00:06:57,230 --> 00:06:58,960
but the world only knows of eight.

163
00:06:58,960 --> 00:06:59,630
The ninth story,

164
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:00,100
it is said,

165
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:02,200
hides the dynasty's greatest secret.

166
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:02,760
Qintian.

167
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:03,800
This talisman

168
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,600
is the last thing Father gave me.

169
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:06,730
He said,

170
00:07:06,730 --> 00:07:08,730
if one day I wake up

171
00:07:08,730 --> 00:07:10,300
and meet someone trustworthy,

172
00:07:10,300 --> 00:07:11,700
I could use this talisman to go to Baiyun Temple

173
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,700
and find Daoist Master Lu Mingyuan.

174
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:16,860
My Lord.

175
00:07:16,860 --> 00:07:17,160
Up there,

176
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,500
someone is coming down the well.

177
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:21,100
Check the other end of the underwater passage.

178
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,130
Dive underwater,

179
00:07:33,130 --> 00:07:34,130
and find another exit.

180
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:35,100
Hurry.

181
00:07:39,230 --> 00:07:40,030
Send a signal.

182
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:41,060
Notify Lord Qin.

183
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,830
The fish are in the net.

184
00:07:43,230 --> 00:07:43,930
Father,

185
00:07:43,930 --> 00:07:45,230
where exactly are you?
